   "Ambrosia Delgard"
  ],
  "finger": {
   "full_name": "Ambrosia Delgard",
   "race": "Human",
   "affiliation": "New Republic",
   "occupation": "Ambassador",
   "homeworld": "Pyrdir",
   "background": "Life before her service to the New Republic isn't something Ambrosia is keen to disclose, but over the years, some snippets have leaked, rumors passed about, and those in the 'need to know' category have become aware.\n\n Her service began on Caspar, as an Aide for Ambassador Dean Corso. Promotion came rather unexpectedly, when he was removed from the picture and she was left to run the Embassy in his stead. Since then, she's negotiated 2 treaties with the CDU, birthed a little girl, become a widow, played a role in the liberation of Corellia, lived a bit of quiet life on Ord Mantel, returned to Caspar with her daughter, and became victim yet again to anti-NR assembly. \n\n This past year has seen her briefly reinstated on Caspar, then homeless, captured, tortured, freed, recovered for a few months, active role in liberating smuggled slaves, participant on NR 20th Anniv gala committee, infected with an alien parasite and recaptured, freed...and now struggling to get a grip on her sanity. Needless to say: it's been a rough one.",
   "quote": ""
  },
